ContentDesc_Das Sternengrab: Here, at the edge of the universe, await as many stories as there are stars in its sea. Of rises and falls, of beginnings and ends...of a little bird who left home with hope, yet nested in sorrow. Hearken unto these tales to be told...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30806_Text: Those who lived and festered, those who died and decayed...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30807_Text: Its people sought ever greater freedoms no matter the cost...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30808_Text: So they created the kindest, most gentle of beasts.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30809_Text: Its steps were light, and its gift was as painless as it was beautiful.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30810_Text: Bathed in its golden glow, they all slept happily ever after...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30812_Text: Once upon a time, there was a beautiful blue star...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30813_Text: ...that fell to pestilence, and rotted inside and out.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30814_Text: The more its people clung to life, the more they suffered.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30815_Text: Until they cursed not the illness, but their fellow corrupted.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30816_Text: And the very last of them wished they had never been born at all.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30817_Text: In a faraway place, a brilliant star eradicated disease...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30818_Text: ...before destroying the selfsame lives it had saved.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30819_Text: They tried to buy peace with fire and steel...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30820_Text: And when one asked, “What is the point?” there were none left to answer.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30821_Text: Farther still existed a star without strife...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30822_Text: ...where none remembered life's trials─or its joys.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30823_Text: What its people had gained from ease, they lost to apathy.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30824_Text: Resuming peace protocol. All life-forms must be eliminated to achieve peace in perpetuity.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30825_Text: Deploying perpetual war machines. Please stand by for order to fire.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_30826_Text: Vital signs detected... Initiating extinction protocol in accordance with primary directive.
npcyell_ids_12290_Text: It means to kill us all!
npcyell_ids_12292_Text: If I can reach the terminal...
npcyell_ids_12294_Text: I did it! I killed them all!
